          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/summersxm/" class=" " title="蘭石">蘭石</a>
                (in Silence and in Hope)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36825180">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">教授尽可把要讲的印出来，也免得 我们天天冒风雪上堂。真真要读书只好在床上，炉旁，烟雾中， 酒瓶边，这才能领略出味道来。所以历来真文豪都是爱逃学的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-12-22 22:01</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
